Airbus Reaches General Agreement With IG Metall Union, FAZ Says

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-10-14T06:13:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/airbus-reaches-general-agreement-with-ig-metall-union-faz-says.html
Airbus SAS has reached a general
agreement with the German labor union IG Metall in a dispute
over future contract terms,  Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung 
reported, citing an interview with Heiko Messerschmidt, a union
spokesman.  The two sides aim to sign an agreement next week, the
newspaper said, citing the spokesman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 